@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ucbqht(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin(0.43))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.30)))
    v1 = 0.37
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v2 + 0.31 - tmp + 0.85)))
    tmp = (0.04 / wp.cos(0.77))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
